title: Morenatsu v 3.5.7z
description:
Morenatsu is an adult kemono yaoi (gay) themed visual novel/dating sim that is Japanese-language. The game centers around the main character going on summer vacation, to be greeted by a selection of kemono males.

The game is still incomplete, so only some of the storylines are playable. At this time, Tatsuki, Kounosuke, Kouya, Shin, Juuichi and Shun are playable, with Soutarou/Kyouji being added together later as a future love triangle. The date is still not confirmed though. 

This is the most recent release of the English translation
please read the 'how to' file before you install this game


Please also note that there will be no further releases as the project has been cancelled
